---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Support LagSync | Secure Checkout"
  description="Support LagSync development — secure donations keep the extension free, private, and up-to-date across browsers.">
  <main class="pt-32 pb-20 flex-grow">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-2xl text-center">
      <div class="inline-block p-4 rounded-2xl bg-cyan-500/10 mb-8 border border-cyan-500/20">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-12 h-12 text-cyan-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9" />
        </svg>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 font-['Space_Mono'] uppercase tracking-tight">
        Fuel the <span class="text-cyan-500">Engine</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 mb-12 leading-relaxed">
        LagSync is built to fix the annoying reality of Bluetooth lag. It's free, private, and ad-free. If it has saved your movie night, choose a tier below to support the development securely via Stripe.
      </p>

      <div class="grid gap-4 mb-16">
        <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/fZuaEX8elfPCboD8T91RC01" target="_blank"
           class="group flex items-center justify-between p-6 bg-[#111] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl hover:border-cyan-500/50 hover:bg-cyan-500/5 transition-all">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-5 text-left">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center text-xl border border-white/10 group-hover:border-cyan-500/30">☕</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-white font-bold font-['Space_Mono']">Buy me a Coffee</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">$5+ — Quick, one-time support.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-white/10 text-white text-sm font-bold rounded-lg group-hover:bg-cyan-500 group-hover:text-black transition-colors">Select</span>
        </a>

        <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/fZubJ19ipbzm8cr0mD1RC00" target="_blank"
           class="group flex items-center justify-between p-6 bg-[#111] border border-cyan-500/20 rounded-2xl hover:border-cyan-500/50 hover:bg-cyan-500/10 transition-all relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-5 text-left">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-cyan-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-xl border border-cyan-500/30">🍕</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-white font-bold font-['Space_Mono']">Buy me a Pizza</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">$15+ — Fuel a late-night coding session.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-cyan-500/20 text-cyan-400 text-sm font-bold rounded-lg group-hover:bg-cyan-500 group-hover:text-black transition-colors">Select</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center items-center gap-6 mb-12 opacity-50 grayscale">
        <span class="text-xs font-['Space_Mono'] uppercase tracking-widest text-white">Secure Checkout by Stripe</span>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-12 border-t border-white/5">
        <h2 class="text-xs font-['Space_Mono'] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500 mb-8">What your support does</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-sm">
          <div>
            <div class="text-cyan-500 mb-2 font-bold">100% Free</div>
            <p class="text-slate-500">Keeps the core features free for everyone.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-cyan-500 mb-2 font-bold">Updates</div>
            <p class="text-slate-500">Funds the constant updates for YouTube & Netflix changes.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-cyan-500 mb-2 font-bold">Privacy</div>
            <p class="text-slate-500">Ensures we never have to sell data or show ads.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
